data.description: Not many homes on the market in Northfield this one could be yours ! Newer Heater 2017,hot water heater 2015,roof 2019,washer and dryer 2020. This rancher is perfect for the family looking for the finest schools,or for retirement without the HOA fees and rules of gated communities. This home offers a large eat in kitchen, oversized fenced in backyard, and a sweet little covered porch. Off street parking for at least 4 cars. Seller is relocating and is looking for an early June closing and would consider a rent back agreement for an earlier settlement. Conveniently located to shopping.Seller MUST find suitable housing.
